events.name: Repair Kopitiam - 26th February 2017
events.description:
Feeling such a waste to throw that standing fan away? Wishing if it's possible to repair them but don't know how?

Come and learn how to repair it with us at our free public event! And understand the importance of repairing before throwing it away!
